casebody.data:
Francis A. GILARDI, et al., petitioners,
v.
DEPARTMENT OF HEALTH AND HUMAN SERVICES, et al. No. 13-567. Supreme Court of the United States July 1, 2014.

Case below, 733 F.3d 1208.

On petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the District of Columbia Circuit. Petition for writ of certiorari granted. Judgment vacated, and case remanded to the United States Court of Appeals for the District of Columbia Circuit for further consideration in light of Burwell v. Hobby Lobby Stores, Inc., 573 U.S. ----, 134 S.Ct. 2751, ---L.Ed.2d ----, 2014 WL 2921709 (2014).
